   <topic>FORM.GET_WIDTH Function</topic>
   <syntax>Width as N = .Get_Width(C format[,P style])</syntax>
   <arguments>
     <argument>
         <name>format</name>
         <description>Character</description>
     </argument>
     <argument>
         <name>style</name>
         <description>Pointer</description>
     </argument>
   </arguments>
   <description>Get width of a layout format.</description>
   <discussion>
The .GET_WIDTH() method returns the Width of a data format in inches, given a display style. Limitations: Desktop applications only.

   </discussion>
  
